# TwelveLabs UI in this project

This demo uses the **published** package — not a local `file:` dependency.

- Package: `@twelvelabs-io/react@0.21.0` (pinned in `app/package.json`)
- Registry auth: `app/.npmrc` + `REGISTRY_TOKEN` from `~/.cursor/secrets/.env.registry` (global) or repo `.env.registry`
- Runtime secrets: `app/.env.local` (`TL_API_KEY`, `KNOWLEDGE_STORE_IDS` only)

When editing UI, follow the **twelvelabs-ui** agent skill (`~/.cursor/skills/twelvelabs-ui/SKILL.md`):

1. Import only from `@twelvelabs-io/react`
2. Use semantic token classes — no hardcoded hex
3. Keep `globals.css` import order: tailwind → tokens → theme
4. Read `node_modules/@twelvelabs-io/react/dist/index.d.mts` for public API

Before `npm install` in `app/`:

```powershell
cd <repo-root>
. .\scripts\load-registry-env.ps1
cd app
npm install
```
